name: r-spacyr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-spacyr
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/spacyr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/spacyr/spacyr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: dc1a4de284fe33bf5d9ecb67b74dc0e61896923913f533f8b97be2a8f9634cac

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-data.table
    - r-reticulate >=1.6
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-data.table
    - r-reticulate >=1.6

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('spacyr')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('spacyr')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://spacyr.quanteda.io
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: An R wrapper to the 'Python' 'spaCy' 'NLP' library, from <http://spacy.io>.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - stevierene82
